Lesson 1.1 - Welcome to your health journey

---------- [L1]

RSS feed link: [insert here]

Creators: Ruth & Nick

Framework:

- Thank you for being here
- Clarify the commitment
- Daily log: Proof of Work (what you did, insights, challenges, important lessons) - timestamping
- Your learning pod
- Your partner (purpose, expectations)
- 20% information: lessons, resources
- 60% mindful experimentation
- 20% reflection  (daily log, synthesis)
- Planning out your journey through behaviour design

Audio lesson notes:
- detailed notes and timestamps from the audio lesson


Experiments (nano to macro)

- Start a log (digital or paper)
- Intention statement: when will I do my daily log each day?
- Accountability (prompts, partner)

- Do a zoom call to meet your partner, learn three interesting things about them
- Say hi to your podmembers in Slack
- Crafting your daily hour (when, where, making up lost days)
- Daily log: Start a notebook, design your daily log into your day

